              Book a Free Call
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg p-5" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--primary)">Try the Calculator</h3>
