      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--primary)">Get expert guidance on your term choice</h2>
      <p class="mb-6" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">A licensed mortgage broker compares all terms across 30+ lenders — always free to use.</p>
